OL,5, Millions of people are set to be worse 
OL,6, off next year amid spiralling costs and
OL,7, tax rises, says an economic think tank.
OL,9,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS) 
OL,10,Fsaid that inflation and higher taxes on
OL,11,Fincomes would negate small wage        
OL,12,Fincreases for middle earners.          
OL,14,FLow-income households will also feel   
OL,15,F"real pain" as the cost of living is   
OL,16,Fset to increase faster than benefit    
OL,17,Fpayments, it said.                     
OL,19,FThe chancellor acknowledged in his     
OL,20,FBudget that families are under strain. 
